            <title>[LOG4J2-947] A new StatusLoggerAdmin listener is added to StatusLogger every time the log is reconfigured</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-947</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When reconfiguring the log the StatusLogger is also reconfigured and every time this is done a new StatusLoggerAdmin is registered on the StatusLogger even if there was already one for this context.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
